/**
 * HELIOS-10: Emerged System
 * 
 * Generated by Emergence Generator from seed "continuity"
 * Session: 1772722665506
 * Spec: 2-fold system enabling lineage emergence and intentional evolution
 * Generation: 1 (parent of future generations)
